{"lemma":"حاجاتٌ","slug":"حاجاتٌ","root":"ح.#.ج","root_slug":"ح-_-ج","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-_-ج","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حاجَة","root":"حوج","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7107","n7123","n9430"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%AC%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"need, necessity (act of needing something)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"need (thing needed)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"neediness, poverty"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"want, desire"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"matter, concern"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"singulative of حَاج (ḥāj, “Alhagi gen. et spp.”)","tags":["form-of","singulative"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Singulative noun composed of حَاج (ḥāj, “Alhagi gen. et spp.”) + ـَة (-a)."},"ipa":["/ħaː.d͡ʒa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7107","headword_ar":"حاجّهُ","root":"Hj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Mgh, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHaAj~apN","text_ar":"مُحَاجَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HijaAjN","text_ar":"حِجَاجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He contended with him in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by, an argument, a plea, an allegation, a proof, an evidence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a testimony."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, TA.) You say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HAj~hu fHaj~ahu","text_ar":"حاجّهُ فحَجَّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He contended with him in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by, an argument,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and he overcame him therein,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thereby."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, * Mgh, Msb.) ―         -b2-  [And hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HAj~","text_ar":"حاجّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He pleaded in a lawsuit."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Mgh","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n7123","headword_ar":"حَاجَّةٌ","root":"Hj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAj~N","text_ar":"حَاجٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places:       -A2-  and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haj~apN","text_ar":"حَجَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n9430","headword_ar":"حَاجَةٌ","root":"Hwj","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, &c.) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAy^ijapN","text_ar":"حَايِجَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AA, IDrd, &c.,) of which latter the former is a contraction, (Kh in the 'Eyn, TA,) or the latter word is unused [except as an epithet, as will be seen below], and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawojaA='u","text_ar":"حَوْجَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, &c.,) are syn. words, of which the meaning is well known: (S, K, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Want; need; necessity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"necessitude; exigency:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [whence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aibonu HaAjapF","text_ar":"اِبْنُ حَاجَةً"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one who is constantly in want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"need:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 143:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAjapN","text_ar":"حَاجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a more general term than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faqorN","text_ar":"فَقْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or each of these terms is more general than the other in some respects, and more particular in others: (TA:) and the former signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing wanted, needed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"required; an object of want, of need,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of exigence; a want; a needful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"requisite, thing, affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"business:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) [and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing to be done, an affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a business:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] pl. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAjN","text_ar":"حَاجٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", [or rather this is a coll. gen. n., of which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAjapN","text_ar":"حَاجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the n. un.,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAjaAtN","text_ar":"حَاجَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [which is of more frequent occurrence,] (S, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiwajN","text_ar":"حِوَجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [which is of rare occurrence,] (S, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawaAy^iju","text_ar":"حَوَايِجُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) which is anomalous, (S, K,) and was disapproved by As, and pronounced by him to be post-classical, but he disapproved it only because of its being anomalous, (S,) and he is said to have retracted his assertion of its being post-classical, (TA,) for it is of frequent occurrence in the [classical] language of the Arabs, (S,) in their verses and in the traditions: (IB, TA:) it seems as though formed from the sing."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAy^ijapN","text_ar":"حَايِجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) which some assert to have been not used; or, accord. to some, it may be pl."},{"kind":"page_break","n":664},{"kind":"text","text":"of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawojaA='u","text_ar":"حَوْجَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", changed from the regular form of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawaAjK","text_ar":"حَوَاجٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawaAjiYu","text_ar":"حَوَاجِىُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHaArK","text_ar":"صَحَارٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", by putting the [elided]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"before the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"j","text_ar":"ج"},{"kind":"text","text":", agreeably with what is often done in the language of the Arabs. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaDaY HaAjatahu","text_ar":"قَضَى حَاجَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He accomplished his want"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) a phrase which signifies [also]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did his business;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he eased nature."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xu*o HaAjataka mina AlT~aEaAmi","text_ar":"خُذْ حَاجَتَكَ مِنَ الطَّعَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Take what thou wantest,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"requirest, of the food"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY nafosiY HaAjapN","text_ar":"فِى نَفْسِى حَاجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAy^ijapN","text_ar":"حَايِجَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawojaA='u","text_ar":"حَوْجَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"In my mind is a want"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (AA, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liY Einoda fulaAnK HaAjapN","text_ar":"لِى عِنْدَ فُلَانٍ حَاجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I want a thing of such a one"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) [When the thing wanted, or not wanted, is mentioned, or referred to by a pronoun, the subst. denoting it, or the pronoun referring to it, is preceded by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY","text_ar":"اـِلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", as in the sayings"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liY HaAjapN A_ilaY ka*aA","text_ar":"لِى حَاجَةٌ اـِلَى كَذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have a want of such a thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA liY A_ilayohi HaAjapN","text_ar":"مَا لِى اـِلَيْهِ حَاجَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have not any want of it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA HaAjatuka A_ilayohi","text_ar":"مَا حَاجَتُكَ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is"},{"kind":"text","text":"the reason of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thy want of it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thy wanting it?"},{"kind":"text","text":"] You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaA lawojaA='u A_il~aA qaDaAhaA","text_ar":"وَلَا لَوْجَا=ءُ اـِلَّا قَضَاهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA baqiYa fiY HawojaA='u","text_ar":"مَا بَقِىَ فِى حَوْجَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There remained not in his bosom a want but he accomplished it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [The dim. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawojaA='u","text_ar":"حَوْجَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuwayojaA='u","text_ar":"حُوَيْجَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": whence the saying,] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA liY fiyhi HawojaA='u","text_ar":"مَا لِى فِيهِ حَوْجَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaA luwayojaA='u","text_ar":"وَلَا لُوَيْجَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaA lawojaA='u walaA HuwayojaA='u","text_ar":"وَلَا لَوْجَا=ءُ وَلَا حُوَيْجَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have no want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nor any little want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with respect to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, S, K.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HawojaA='u","text_ar":"حَوْجَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below.] In the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hujo Hujay~aAka","text_ar":"حُجْ حُجَيَّاكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Seek the little thing that thou wantest"},{"kind":"text","text":"], it seems that the second and third radical letters of the latter word [originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HuwayojaA='aka","text_ar":"حُوَيْجَا=ءَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] have been transposed [and that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HujayowaA='aka","text_ar":"حُجَيْوَا=ءَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"has been then changed into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hujay~aAka","text_ar":"حُجَيَّاكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IDrd, AAF, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA tarakotu mino HaAjapK walaA","text_ar":"مَا تَرَكْتُ مِنْ حَاجَةٍ وَلَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAjapK","text_ar":"دَاجَةٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I left not any act of disobedience to which I was enticed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA from a trad. [But see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAjapN","text_ar":"دَاجَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dwj","text_ar":"دوج"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","A","Msb","IB"]}]}}